Orion Capital Managers, L.P.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 3:51 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Orion Capital Managers, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Orion Capital Managers, L.P. is a real estate investment firm specializing in commercial real estate investment management. The company invests in various assets, including offices, high street retail properties, shopping centers, warehouses and distribution centers, hotels, and residential properties. It makes investments in Europe with a focus on France, Central London, Germany, Italy, Spain, Scandinavia and the United Kingdom. Orion Capital Managers, L.P. was founded in 1999 and is based in London, the United Kingdom with additional offices in Milan, Italy; Munich, Germany; Madrid, Spain; and Paris, France.


2 Cavendish SquareLondon,  W1G OPEUnited KingdomFounded in 1999



Phone: 44 20 7612 9399

Fax: 44 20 7612 9398

www.orioncapitalmanagers.com







